==Indonesian==
===Etymology===
Common Oceanic, compare Fijian ''[[taci]]''
===Noun===
'''adik'''

# [[younger]] ([[brother]]/[[sister]]) ''([[sibling]])''

====Usage====
* "Adik [[laki-laki]]" is used to mean "younger brother".
* "Adik [[perempuan]]" is used to mean "younger sister".

